channel.title: First Post As a First Greeting For All
channel.description: Hello Ladies/ Gentlemen... It is my pleasure to write the first time here. I feel happy to read your posts and exchange ideas with you. I am a representative for non-government organization based in Yemen. I look forward to benefit from your ideas and experience in humanity working, to help my society and all people around the world. Again, it is very honored to write here and you read oh my best friends.

item.title: First Post As a First Greeting For All
item.dc:creator: Rohini_Simbodyal
item.description:
We are delighted to welcome you to IATI Discuss. We hope that you find this forum a useful way to gain further information and network with IATI’s community.

All the best,
Rohini
